Package: nprobust
Type: Package
Title: Nonparametric Robust Estimation and Inference Methods using Local Polynomial Regression and Kernel Density Estimation
Version: 0.5.0
Date: 2025-04-12
Authors@R: c(person(given = c("Sebastian"),
